1.docker run -d -p 5000:5000 --net=host --restart=always --name registry registry
   
  Note: images are stored in /var/lib/registry/docker/registry/v2/repositories
  
2. config docker deamon to connect to the private registry via /etc/sysconfig/docker
   eg:
      OPTIONS="-g /opt/scs/docker --insecure-registry 10.11.150.76:6000"
      
